"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/67/206779.jpg","floor":"#5-11","id":"1501369","time":"2019-9-29 23:34","userId":"zq0504032","userName":"满舰饰假子","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">rnono</span> 说: 本来只觉得是猛台词的<br>去了次香港后发现 这两个中间是海</q></div>23333可以把小汽船也砍了"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/32/60/326025.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1500891","time":"2019-9-28 23:43","userId":"seikai","userName":"疾風迅雷のナイトハルト","userSign":"","message":"可爱即是正义","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/47/144774.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1500896","time":"2019-9-28 23:49","userId":"saltymoe","userName":"Kanayo","userSign":"(卖萌の闲货.ver2)","message":"洛丽塔是少女 日本文化中的洛丽塔是指穿衣上的少女风格 （甚至有点幼女）但是并不是洛丽塔穿的衣服出来的洛丽塔风格 而是由欧洲的洛可可风格 一种繁复充满曲线的风格 演变而来的 而欧洲的洛可可风格也收到中国风的影响的<br><br><br>emmm我还是顺序说吧<br><br>首先洛可可是在巴洛克的风格上发展起来的，这些风格一般都是指建筑的，后来才在服装上发展，就是说那几个教堂啊啥的也可以是洛可可风格的，不单止服装。然后还受到过一定中国风的影响，当然也是建筑啊园林设计啊包括服装等方面采用中国样式。（到这里觉得中国流行洛可可也很正常吧）然后《洛丽塔》问世，到了日本后人们就用萝莉来称呼少女（这个阿宅喜闻乐见），同时因为洛可可是一个“白日梦”那样奢靡的时代，所以服装有很多花边啊细褶啊装饰，虽然到了日本以后就成了“轻飘飘”，但在《下妻物语》中，女主解释道穿洛丽塔风格的衣服就是想要回到那个无忧无虑的年代。洛可可的轻飘飘少女心，加上洛丽塔的萝莉，一拍即合。<br><br>不知道科普到没有（服装专业学生强势装逼<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/62.gif\" smileid=\"101\" alt=\"(bgm85)\">）","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/42/334255.jpg","floor":"#7-1","id":"1500907","time":"2019-9-29 00:13","userId":"334255","userName":"烧鳗事变🔮","userSign":"","message":"bangumi还能遇到服装专业的哇塞，我也是，来握个手！"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/26/342667.jpg","floor":"#7-2","id":"1500910","time":"2019-9-29 00:15","userId":"342667","userName":"鋭ちゃん","userSign":"","message":"啊咧咧...我也觉得洛丽塔的着装很洛可可...看上去"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/47/144774.jpg","floor":"#7-3","id":"1500912","time":"2019-9-29 00:18","userId":"saltymoe","userName":"Kanayo","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">烧鳗事变&#x1F9F8;</span> 说: bangumi还能遇到服装专业的哇塞，我也是，来握个手！</q></div>万能班固米哈哈哈握爪^^"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/47/144774.jpg","floor":"#7-4","id":"1500914","time":"2019-9-29 00:21","userId":"saltymoe","userName":"Kanayo","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">鋭ちゃん</span> 说: 啊咧咧...我也觉得洛丽塔的着装很洛可可...看上去</q></div>好眼力！"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/26/342667.jpg","floor":"#7-5","id":"1500918","time":"2019-9-29 00:30","userId":"342667","userName":"鋭ちゃん","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Shiyo</span> 说: 好眼力！</q></div>对洛可可的印象就只有《秋千》这幅画<br><img src=\"https://www.artandobject.com/sites/default/files/styles/gallery_item/public/20111211141349fragonardtheswing.jpg?h=e6e37fb1&itok=1NUUS0DC\" class=\"code\" alt><br><br>不过因为洛可可和巴洛克很像，巴洛克听多了自然会脑补到洛可可..."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/67/206779.jpg","floor":"#7-6","id":"1500935","time":"2019-9-29 01:04","userId":"zq0504032","userName":"满舰饰假子","userSign":"","message":"罗锅锅变成洛丽塔也是可以<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>话说罗锅锅和哥特也不是一码事吧。。所谓哥特萝莉什么的。。。<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/82/18215.jpg","floor":"#7-7","id":"1500969","time":"2019-9-29 01:27","userId":"utar","userName":"塔塔塔","userSign":"","message":"棒棒哒"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/47/144774.jpg","floor":"#7-8","id":"1501130","time":"2019-9-29 12:57","userId":"saltymoe","userName":"Kanayo","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">鋭ちゃん</span> 说: 对洛可可的印象就只有《秋千》这幅画<br><br><br>不过因为洛可可和巴洛克很像，巴洛克听多了自然会脑补到洛可可...</q></div>这就是洛可可风格最明显主要的一幅呀~"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/47/144774.jpg","floor":"#7-9","id":"1501131","time":"2019-9-29 12:59","userId":"saltymoe","userName":"Kanayo","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">满舰饰假子</span> 说: 罗锅锅变成洛丽塔也是可以<br>话说罗锅锅和哥特也不是一码事吧。。所谓哥特萝莉什么的。。。</q></div>拜占庭→哥特→文艺复兴→巴洛克→洛可可<br><br>哥特也能洛丽塔跟当时朋克在日本的流行也有点关系的样子，可能是哥特和朋克都有死亡的元素吧？的感觉（口胡）"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/14/131492.jpg","floor":"#7-10","id":"1501197","time":"2019-9-29 17:48","userId":"misakaxindex","userName":"東瀬まつり太","userSign":"","message":"洛可可+1 不过怎么会用洛丽塔这个名字而不是洛可可呢"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/47/144774.jpg","floor":"#7-11","id":"1501236","time":"2019-9-29 19:37","userId":"saltymoe","userName":"Kanayo","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">東瀬まつり太</span> 说: 洛可可+1 不过怎么会用洛丽塔这个名字而不是洛可可呢</q></div>因为《洛丽塔》里的少女形象吧 事实上Lo娘们不也总是被说都多大了还穿那种小女孩穿的衣服 之类的？"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/61/36176.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1500922","time":"2019-9-29 00:31","userId":"36176","userName":"豆沙包罐头","userSign":"(事到如今数不完了呀)","message":"语义在传播过程中被曲解是这样的","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/16/331630.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1500930","time":"2019-9-29 00:56","userId":"wudiangongyuan","userName":"五点共圆","userSign":"(科气严重，缺乏妹子)","message":"传播之后就不是原本的东西了。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/89/258942.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1501156","time":"2019-9-29 15:01","userId":"258942","userName":"[ > . < ]","userSign":"(正在死亡)","message":"每次看到洛丽塔，大脑都会读成萝莉塔，这又是为什么","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/67/206779.jpg","floor":"#10-1","id":"1501194","time":"2019-9-29 17:39","userId":"zq0504032","userName":"满舰饰假子","userSign":"","message":"覅紧个，英语又没有声调<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1501160","time":"2019-9-29 15:15","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"(媛娇系是检验大法的唯一标准)","message":"是的啊 原著党生存艰难很容易就被婆罗门化啊","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/67/206779.jpg","floor":"#11-1","id":"1501193","time":"2019-9-29 17:39","userId":"zq0504032","userName":"满舰饰假子","userSign":"","message":"<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/32/16/321614.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1501167","time":"2019-9-29 15:30","userId":"321614","userName":"lowbrow","userSign":"(一个无趣的人)","message":"“别人的痛苦才是你艺术的源泉；而你去受苦，只会成为别人的艺术源泉”---王小波","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#12-1","id":"1501200","time":"2019-9-29 17:54","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"","message":"+1"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/14/131492.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1501198","time":"2019-9-29 17:51","userId":"misakaxindex","userName":"東瀬まつり太","userSign":"([s]安静点格子[/s])","message":"<img src=\"https://i3.hoopchina.com.cn/hupuapp/bbs/964/39146964/thread_39146964_20190428234627_s_60751_w_450_h_338_88587.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800/format,webp\" class=\"code\" alt><br>这个表情包也是类似的情况，这个人本来打捞溺死学生尸体，之后要求加价否则不给人的时候拍的这么一张照片","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/89/258942.jpg","floor":"#13-1","id":"1501226","time":"2019-9-29 19:05","userId":"258942","userName":"[ > . < ]","userSign":"","message":"然后他出来辟谣了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/14/131492.jpg","floor":"#13-2","id":"1501248","time":"2019-9-29 20:13","userId":"misakaxindex","userName":"東瀬まつり太","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q>命名问题<br>“萝莉塔风格”一词，源自弗拉基米尔·納博科夫的出名小说《萝莉塔》（Lolita），而萝莉塔服装一般亦为年轻人所穿着，但是支持萝莉塔服装的人并不认为以“Lolita”为这种服装命名，会带有性方面的意味。事实上，很多日本人在未有接触一些有关萝莉塔服装的刊物，例如《Gothic & Lolita Bible》以前，也不知道这个名字的起源，与小说《萝莉塔》有关。支持萝莉塔服装的人，很多时都将自己的打扮，与儿童或小娃娃看齐，并认为应该看来“可爱”、“美丽”与“优雅”，多于“性感”。<br><br>日本文化比西方更注重年轻化的外观与行为，而很多日本的成年女性，也非常喜欢甚至购买一些在西方被视为以儿童为对象的产品，如Hello Kitty等。有人认为，萝莉塔也是这种杰斗现象的一种形象化延伸。</q></div>发现维基百科上对于这个命名问题记录的很全面了，日语的版本记录更为全面，不过太长了没仔细看"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/42/244287.jpg","floor":"#14","id":"1501230","time":"2019-9-29 19:28","userId":"muon","userName":"muon","userSign":"(Time is not your enemy, forever is)","message":"一直认为一种流行范式只有被观察到后才会被赋予一个适合的符号","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/44/26/442614.jpg","floor":"#15","id":"1501247","time":"2019-9-29 20:11","userId":"longlivel5i","userName":"trivedy","userSign":"","message":"萝莉and洛丽塔=雷锋and雷峰塔","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/44/14410.jpg","floor":"#16","id":"1501342","time":"2019-9-29 23:03","userId":"wakarewa","userName":"ykcop","userSign":"(我是自愿上学的)","message":"<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">这个问题困扰我好几年了 作为一个纳博科夫 伪 脑残粉<br>后来我发现很多喜欢萝莉塔装的人，其实没有读过洛丽塔。<br><span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">从此释怀：哦，就这样吧。</span><br><span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">我的洛是我的洛</span>","sub":[]}]